<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-61-0212 </DOCNO><TEXT>This bibliography contains citations concerning the occurance and effectsof asbestos and silicate pollution outside of the workplace. Topics includeincreased cancer risk associated with asbestos pollution, and the hazardsof silica-dust inhalation and silicate effects on water resources. Includedare pollutant sources, and sampling techniques and test results of analysesof indoor air samples, drinking water, and ground water for these pollutants.Asbestos and silicate pollution in the workplace and asbestos-removaltechnology are considered in other bibliographies. (This updated bibliographycontains 378 citations, none of which are new entries to the previousedition.)</TEXT></DOC>